# Server-side secrets for local dev (Cloudflare runtime via platformProxy).
# Copy to `.dev.vars` and fill in. NEVER commit the real file.

# Fastmail API token with "Email" + "Email Submission" scopes.
# Create at: Fastmail → Settings → Privacy & Security → API tokens.
FASTMAIL_API_TOKEN=""

# Verified Fastmail address to send AS (must match an account identity).
MAIL_FROM="you@acme.example"

# Where leads are delivered (can be the same as MAIL_FROM).
MAIL_TO="you@acme.example"

# Cloudflare Turnstile secret key. Leave blank to disable the spam check locally.
# Always-pass test secret: 1x0000000000000000000000000000000AA
TURNSTILE_SECRET_KEY="1x0000000000000000000000000000000AA"
